Summary:
packet.summary

Text:
packet.show

Command to recreate:
packet.command

PDF:
packet.psdump(tempfile.mkdtemp())
(clean up after)

For windows:
  start /path/to/file, shell=True
For OSX:
  open /path/to/file
For linux:
  xdg-open /path/to/file

